By: Sheikh 'Abd-el-Hadi ben Ridouane
---
Any man who does not let himself be guided by a spiritual director is
guilty of rebellion towards God, for without a guide he could not
obtain access to the road of salvation, were he to possess by memory a
thousand works of theology.
